{"tid":1202852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(野餐必備) 頭先去咗幫大家搜羅必備物資","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T05:27:46.000Z","uid":176442,"like":153,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"97407ceb391625435e4cde5cdeb50ac7cfe9f218","tid":1202852,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"去野餐可能大家無咩經驗<br />\n所以去咗超級市場睇吓有咩好嘢啱野餐 介紹比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先保鮮紙同手套呢啲必備啦<br />\n唔使教喇掛？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzRfA1p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzRfA1p.png&h=7cde6ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過呢啲手套要嚟搬嘢絕對唔啱使<br />\n都係去五金舖買啲防𠝹手加硬嗰啲<br />\n保護到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSzdnGq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSzdnGq.png&h=18b0314a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後緊係汽水啦 鋁罐裝唔易爛<br />\n又啱大家開心飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過痴立立 小心啲飲！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYiE2CY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYiE2CY.png&h=6285a446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提神緊係唔少得咖啡 你知野餐可以玩好耐<br />\n特別介紹以下品牌 因為都係特別硬淨<br />\n<strong>點撞都無咁易撞爛</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufPAAYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufPAAYg.png&h=b6e3ca5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下幾隻真係硬到無朋友 <br />\n<strong>無咁易撞凹 推介</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kDapRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kDapRC.png&h=dca3fe85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7id2fYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7id2fYh.png&h=350a1fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有人人識嘅雀巢 一樣夠硬淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHwLdNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHwLdNT.png&h=80ab8a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罐頭美食當然唔少得啦 有大有細<br />\n鐘意食咩咪買咩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iC6HEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iC6HEy.png&h=a3652951&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXjH0re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXjH0re.png&h=89090a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人食嘅當然都有比狗食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zW0gkrF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzW0gkrF.png&h=11e48e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjyYyPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjyYyPM.png&h=ccde533e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>延伸閱讀：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199438/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199438/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n糖水要嚟搽麵包食又得<br />\n沖嘢飲都得<br />\n<strong>不過真係要小心唔好倒瀉 成身癡立立就煩</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ha9Eidy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fha9Eidy.png&h=f53fe293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有噴霧裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xm2qYea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxm2qYea.png&h=30c04771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食油一樣不可缺少<br />\n欖油要嚟撈下沙律咁幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花生油嗰啲不時之需啦<br />\n點知會唔會想炒吓菜食<br />\n<strong>不過真係唔好倒瀉落地呀 好麻煩架！！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ToBSDfz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FToBSDfz.png&h=87bbb7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91Wy68V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91Wy68V.png&h=598d8699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後見到鐵絲網 無特別架買定下次bbq用啫<br />\n不過啲邊位小心𠝹手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExYURBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExYURBm.png&h=a39e53d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐘意野餐嘅巴打大家都一齊分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810d8474437f8755eaf4830cbf40a70ce653b119","tid":1202852,"uid":251510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china?recruiter=554231063&amp;recruited_by_id=92a49e10-2e1d-11e6-bc11-b193dd1d0f73&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_term=address_book&amp;share_bandit_exp=message-15727601-en-GB&amp;share_bandit_var=v0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extraditi